    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349950/extras/7416f4ba5ba0c1b5bbc3fe9c42a750fb.avif?t=1764702842\" width=600 height=92 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About:</strong></h2>Riddles &amp; Sieges is a medieval puzzle game where you use old siege weapons to solve puzzles.<br><br><br>Each building works and attacks differently. For example catapult shoots over a tile. Trebuchet does the same, but has a delay before attacking. And ballista only attacks when being destroyed.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349950/extras/a064ac9f00df7928c8db857fdb20a387.poster.avif?t=1764702842\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349950/extras/a064ac9f00df7928c8db857fdb20a387.webm?t=1764702842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349950/extras/a064ac9f00df7928c8db857fdb20a387.mp4?t=1764702842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The game features:</strong></h2>- 55 handcrafted levels with each one being harder than the previous<br><br>- A lot different mechanics that keep you interested throughout the whole game<br>- Custom Level Editor if you want to create levels of your own and share them with everyone!<br>- Calming atmosphere that keeps you relaxed while solving the puzzles",
